At this point, my opponent wrote to me:  "I think I've just about given away any advantage I may have had earlier. Your material superiority and active Queen should give you an easy win now. Well played."  I wonder if he was using psychology on me as once I heard I should have an easy win, I immediately became nervous.  I encouraged him to play on as I have lost games with better advantage and he cheerfully agreed to do so.
